.env

# ── Raw data caches: contain focal-point names & phone numbers ─────────
_cache_kobo.json
_cache_zite.json

# ── Source datasets (not for publication; obtain through the cluster) ──
Master List/
Site verifcation_Demographic/
IOM_data Submission/
Somali Maps/

# ── Internal pipeline docs (reference internal endpoints/asset UIDs) ───
CCCM_Q2_Dashboard_FULL_PROMPT.md
README_pipeline.md

# ── Invalidated artefacts from a failed early run ──────────────────────
*.INVALID.json
*.INVALID.csv

# ── Local build metadata ───────────────────────────────────────────────
_build_stats.json
__pycache__/

.vercel
# public/index.html IS committed — Vercel's GitHub integration builds from the repo,
# so the deployable artefact must be tracked (kept in sync by the daily workflow).
